            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1720624525296-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>creamy stock </strong>to the pan with the <strong>chopped basa</strong>, a squeeze of <strong>lemon juice</strong> (save the rest for later!) and a generous grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>fish pie filling</strong></p><p>Transfer the <strong>fish pie filling</strong> an <strong>oven-proof dish</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
